item.title: Need a coder quickyl for commands and to delete some npc's and to move them
item.dc:creator: @Gidedin Gidedin
item.description:
@Gidedin wrote:

Like they say, just go to Autospawn.cfg and look for the NPC id, select all line and delete.

Here go a example:

If you want delete the Shop Assistent, look for:

spawn = 523

And delete all this line:

spawn = 523	3217	3416	0	0	0	0	0	1	Varrock General Store Shop Assistant

Done, your Varrock General Store Shop Assistant now are deleted.

item.title: Need a coder quickyl for commands and to delete some npc's and to move them
item.dc:creator: @Gidedin Gidedin
item.description:
@Gidedin wrote:

Well i dont read all the post, just go there:

http://java.sun.com/javase/downloads/index_jdk5.jsp

And clock on the:

JDK 5.0 Update 11

Download it and in and install, now, go to your compile and change all to this:

@echo off COLOR 07 echo Compiling... title StrikerServer Client "C:\Program Files\java\jdk1.5.0_11\bin\javac.exe" -cp . *.java pause

And, in your RunServer, change to this:

@echo off color 09 title StrikerServer java -Xmx512m -cp .;./jython.jar;./MySql/mysql-connector-java-3.0.08-ga-bin.jar server

Done, just compile, if u get this menssage:

Compiling... Note: stream.java uses or overrides a deprecated API. Note: Recompile with -Xlint:deprecation for details.

Your compile is working.
